data.description: NEW Fairway Collection ''Wakefield E'' Plan by Lennar Homes located in the New Master Planned community Artavia! The beautiful 2-story Wakefield plan by Lennar features an entry foyer, a dining room, a kitchen with breakfast room that offers access to a relaxing covered rear patio, a generous open family room, and a walk-in utility room. The primary bedroom features an en suite primary bathroom with dual sinks, stand-up shower, private toilet enclosure, and access to a large primary closet. The beautiful community of Artavia will offer residents everything from a delicious community cafe, fitness center, splash pad and playground, to discovery ponds, relaxing green spaces, a sparkling five-acre lake and a boardwalk.
